dt-option.default:
        The default value for the `-init searchPanes.collapse` paramater is `false`. This means that as standard the panes will be visible when the page is loaded. 


        As standard, SearchPanes will display the panes on start up.

        By setting the `-init searchPanes.collapse` option to true, they will be collapsed on start up and can be viewed by pressing the 'show panes' button.





$(document).ready(function() {
    $('#example').DataTable( {
        searchPanes:{
            collapse: true
        },
        dom: 'Sfrtip',
    });
});
